Revision history for WWW-SFDC

0.1     2015-01-27
        Lots of breaking changes:
        
        - Renamed Login.pm => SessionManager.pm
        - All SOAP::Lite interaction now goes through SessionManager->_call().
        - SessionManager->_call() catches an INVALID_SESSION_ID error and regenerates it.
        - Role::Session provides a transparent interface to SessionManager to
          Tooling, Metadata and Partner.
        - Creds merged into one creds() attribute, handled by Role::Session.

0.021   2015-01-15
        Make debugging for Tooling.pm optional!

0.02    2015-01-14
        Flesh out Tooling.pm a little.

0.01    2015-01-14
        First version.